    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Still和Moving可以互相切换。AuthVault是Still的一个分支出口，相当于静态状态下的认证检查。另外Crash要特殊标注，这是严重故障状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Still",
        "Moving",
        "FinTech_AuthVault",
        "Crash"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我先把主体结构画出来：PaymentGateway指向Still，Still分出两条线到AuthVault和Moving，Moving回连Still，同时Moving指向Crash，Crash再连到FraudDetection。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway",
        "Still",
        "FinTech_AuthVault",
        "Moving",
        "Crash",
        "FinTech_FraudDetection"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "样式上需要区分一下：Still用白色填充表示静止；Moving和Crash用斜体表示运动相关；Crash特别重要，要用红色背景、白色粗体字，黄色边框加粗。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Still",
        "Moving",
        "Crash",
        "classDef notMoving",
        "classDef movement",
        "classDef badBadEvent"
